release_note: Added possibility to share a drawing.
Updated cards design on Boards screen. Increased maximum zoom scale for the canvas.
Some bug fixes for the Adding Space indicator.
Now additional space isn t added automatically you have to drag an indicator until it becomes green.
Add different segments for boards. Further drawing zoom in out. Multiple windows support. Thumbnails on Boards screen. Content menus for boards. Bug fixes.
UI improvements when in dark mode.
